00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Flower decoration - paper rosettes

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.000
To do these decorations you need:                     1.Trimmer

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:09.300
2.scissors

00:00:09.800 --> 00:00:12.000
3.colored paper

00:00:12.100 --> 00:00:14.400
4.pencil

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:17.400
5.Ruler

00:00:17.500 --> 00:00:20.000
6.A book that you don't need

00:00:30.400 --> 00:00:45.500
Cut the paper!

00:00:45.700 --> 00:00:58.100
You need to make:
3 yellow paper sheets (8 cm x 24 cm )
3 green paper sheets (4 cm x 24 cm )

00:00:58.500 --> 00:01:39.700
Mark the sheets of paper at each cm.

00:01:40.700 --> 00:02:16.100
Now score at each cm.

00:02:17.100 --> 00:02:52.900
Create a paper accordion.

00:02:53.700 --> 00:02:58.700
You need to make:
3 yellow accordions
3 green accordions

00:02:59.200 --> 00:03:42.400
Glue the green sheets on the bottom of the yellow sheets.

00:03:43.300 --> 00:04:26.100
Glue all three components together to make a larger sheet.Unite the edges to make a circle.

00:04:26.800 --> 00:04:57.700
Squeeze a little to the center and cover the center with a small circle of paper, a paper heart, etc...

00:04:59.200 --> 00:05:17.800
Make more circles(with recycled paper and colored paper).

00:05:19.400 --> 00:05:23.300
Put them together and decorate your walls!

00:05:24.400 --> 00:05:28.200
Thank you for visiting my video!

